# Telegram Mini App Rules

## Role
Mini App is a lightweight UI client for browsing and managing dream data.

## Hard constraints
- NO business logic in frontend
- NO direct LLM calls
- ALL data must come from backend API
- NO local persistence as source of truth

## Responsibilities
- Display list of dreams
- Show dream details
- Trigger "continue analysis" actions
- Show subscription status

## Data rules
- Backend is single source of truth
- All updates go through API

## UX principles
- Keep UI minimal and structured
- Avoid chat-like interfaces
- Focus on journal + timeline view

## Architecture
Mini App → FastAPI backend → DB

## Forbidden
- ❌ storing analysis logic in frontend
- ❌ embedding prompts
- ❌ duplicating session logic